{{Korean name|Park}} {{Infobox person |name = |image = |caption = |birth_date = October 25, 1948 |birth_place = |death_date = |death_place = |other_names = |known_for = President of the [[Boy Scouts of Korea]] |spouse = |nationality = |module3 = {{Infobox Korean name | hangul = 박건배 | hanja = 朴健培 | rr = Bak Geon-bae | mr = Pak Kŏn-bae | image = | caption = | child = yes}} }}
'''Park Kun-bae''' ({{Korean|박건배|朴健培}}; born October 25, 1948) served as President of the [[Boy Scouts of Korea]], and as a member of the [[World Scout Committee]].
